mode: (printf with 9 x tab)
printf "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGotcha"
works ok, while one tab more
printf "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGotcha"
doesn't work (it doesn't print Gotcha
at column 80, but at column 131).
